cars.description: The Polestar 2 is a sleek and futuristic electric hatchback with a spacious and luxurious interior, a high-tech infotainment system, and a powerful performance package.
The Suzuki Swift is a small and agile hatchback with a fuel-efficient engine, a sporty design, and a practical cabin.
The Mitsubishi ASX is a versatile and reliable crossover SUV with a roomy interior, a smooth ride, and a user-friendly touchscreen.
The Hyundai i30 is a stylish and comfortable hatchback with a peppy engine, a spacious trunk, and a generous warranty.
The Toyota Corolla is a popular and dependable sedan with a refined engine, a smooth transmission, and a suite of advanced safety features.
The Toyota Camry is a spacious and well-rounded sedan with a powerful engine, a comfortable ride, and a high-quality interior.
The Audi Q3 is a subcompact luxury SUV with a turbocharged engine, nimble handling, and a premium cabin.
The Nissan X Trail is a compact SUV with a spacious interior, a large cargo area, and an optional third row of seats.
The Subaru Forester is a rugged and capable SUV with a standard all-wheel drive system, a spacious cabin, and a high ground clearance.
The Audi Q5 is a compact luxury SUV with a powerful engine, a smooth ride, and an upscale interior with a built-in GPS system.
The Mazda CX 9 is a midsize SUV with a turbocharged engine, a sporty handling, and a refined interior with three rows of seats.
The Audi Q7 is a midsize luxury SUV with a potent engine, a composed ride, and an elegant interior with three rows of seats and many features.
The Mistsubishi Pajero Sport GLX is a midsize SUV with a diesel engine, a four-wheel drive system, and a rugged design.
The Toyota Landcruiser Prado is a large SUV with a powerful engine, a four-wheel drive system, and an off-road capability.
The Kia Carnival is a large minivan with a spacious interior, a sliding door on each side, and many family-friendly features.
The Mercedes Benz V Class is a large minivan with a luxurious interior, a diesel engine, and an optional all-wheel drive system.
